    You can download this again, any time by logging into your  <%= link_to "your account", show_user_url(@user.id) %>.
	<br>
	<br>
	Enjoy the music! <br>
	<%= @artist.name %> <br>

	This email is powered by <a href="http://www.threerepeater.com" >Three Repeater</a>. <br>
	The complete DIY Artist solution
